name: The Beginning- Legend Awakens
description:
It has began.
After being asleep for nearly for 25 centuries, the legend has awakened. The Druid Lord- Kal Thazard finally rises up from his burial ground. It was predicted in the ages of the God that when the Earth would need its hero, someone worthy would be chosen and he would rise from the realms unkonwn to the humans. The prophecy has been fullfilled. The legendary Scorpion King who was feared by the entire Globe now raises as some unknown danger starts to lurk its shadow on the Planet.
